<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>13 SPEED AND 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-713/18 SERIES - INSTALL - OUTPUT YOKE/COMPANION FLANGE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>OUTPUT YOKE/COMPANION FLANGE</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>You must remove the shifter housing to lock the transmission.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Engage two (2) mainshaft sliding clutches into two (2) mainshaft gears to lock the
                transmission (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007q6">Figure 266</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007q6" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007q6" filename="../figg13/G13007Q6.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 266. Engage Mainshaft Sliding Clutches into Mainshaft Gears</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the speedometer drive gear rotor or replacement spacer on the output shaft inside
                the rear bearing cover (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007q7">Figure 267</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007q7" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007q7" filename="../figg13/G13007Q7.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 267. Slide Companion Flange or Yoke onto Output Shaft</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If the slinger on the yoke is damaged, replace using a Slinger/Seal kit (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007q7">Figure 267</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Slide the companion flange or yoke onto the output shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007q7">Figure 267</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the output shaft nut; tighten to 450 to 500 ft-lbs. (610 to 678 N&#183;m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007q8">Figure 268</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007q8" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007q8" filename="../figg13/G13007Q8.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 268. Install Output Shaft Nut</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Unlock the transmission.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
